text: Meike Holländer (born 18 January 1965) is a German rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1988 Summer Olympics for West Germany. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:West German female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of West Germany Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bremerhaven
